_sText:
'New' version of my very first bad looking Jail Break map. The map was redone from scratch and many stuff is changed or new. Enjoy and feel free to leave any feedback.

Map Features
------------------
- 24T 16CT spawns
- Overview
- Custom textures
- Custom particles
- Random usp and grenade in cells
- Minigames
    - Soccer
    - Volleyball
    - Jumping
    - Climb
    - Crushers & spikes
    - Bomb toss
    - Disco
    - Simon says
    - 1 block is safe
    - Breaking blocks
